  "original_title": "\u0d94\u0dc3\u0dca\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dda\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dc4 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dad \u0d89\u0dc4\u0dc5 \u0db1\u0d82\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Australian central bank is also raising interest rates",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Reserve Bank of Australia (RBA) has raised the country's policy interest rate by 50 basis points.",
        "There, foreign reports indicate that the basic interest rate has been increased to 1.35%.",
        "This action has been taken with the aim of stabilizing the Australian economy in the face of global economic fluctuations."
      ],
